WEBVTT

00:00:13.888 --> 00:00:16.224
(2025, Present, Autumn)
(To you who forgot me.)

00:00:20.437 --> 00:00:22.272
Who are you?

00:00:24.357 --> 00:00:25.483
Do you know me?

00:00:27.402 --> 00:00:28.153
(Well,)

00:00:29.279 --> 00:00:30.363
(I am Gi Haneul.)

00:00:32.704 --> 00:00:33.824
Who

00:00:33.824 --> 00:00:34.909
are you?

00:00:41.708 --> 00:00:43.376
It's hard to say

00:00:43.752 --> 00:00:45.420
when his memories will return.

00:01:00.704 --> 00:01:02.896
(It might never come back.)

00:01:05.774 --> 00:01:09.277
(Why did you forget me?)

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:18.745
You're Yeo Saebyeok, not Gi Haneul?

00:01:19.704 --> 00:01:21.456
What is your relationship?

00:01:22.582 --> 00:01:25.251
Haneul can't cooperate
with the investigation right now.

00:01:25.502 --> 00:01:26.836
So I came in his place.

00:01:30.381 --> 00:01:32.608
That's tricky.

00:01:32.759 --> 00:01:34.592
I'm the person closest to Haneul,

00:01:34.592 --> 00:01:36.192
and I was also a witness that day.

00:01:36.679 --> 00:01:38.139
You can just talk to me.

00:01:38.848 --> 00:01:40.266
From now on, contact me.

00:01:41.059 --> 00:01:41.810
First,

00:01:42.060 --> 00:01:43.853
we're investigating a hit-and-run case.

00:01:44.352 --> 00:01:47.565
But it may not be a simple one.

00:01:47.982 --> 00:01:48.525
What?

00:01:48.733 --> 00:01:51.694
There was no surveillance at the scene,
so there isn't much information.

00:01:51.986 --> 00:01:55.365
The car involved was found
in an empty lot nearby.

00:01:56.616 --> 00:01:58.409
The registered owner is

00:01:59.160 --> 00:02:00.912
Lee Seri.

00:02:02.038 --> 00:02:03.039
Lee Seri?

00:02:03.289 --> 00:02:04.916
You know her, right?

00:02:15.885 --> 00:02:17.428
(Main symptoms of dissociative amnesia)
(No matter which stories you forgot)

00:02:18.513 --> 00:02:21.099
(or which ones you rewrote...)

00:02:50.420 --> 00:02:54.465
(I'll always stay on the last page
of that book.)

00:02:58.050 --> 00:03:01.010
A WeTV ORIGINAL SERIES

00:03:02.590 --> 00:03:04.760
GI HANEUL
HWANG JUNSU

00:03:08.270 --> 00:03:09.480
IN ASSOCIATION WITH YYDS

00:03:11.060 --> 00:03:14.020
YEO SAEBYEOK
LEE JAWOON

00:03:20.450 --> 00:03:23.110
YOON JUNGHAN
OH JAEHYEONG

00:03:24.320 --> 00:03:26.580
LEE SERI
PARK EUNJO

00:03:31.502 --> 00:03:39.344
=Never Forget Your Enemy=

00:03:39.344 --> 00:03:44.682
=Episode 4=
(Walking Through Memories)

00:03:49.354 --> 00:03:50.355
What do you want to say?

00:03:51.481 --> 00:03:53.816
(2018, Seven Years Ago, Autumn)

00:03:53.816 --> 00:03:54.496
You don't know?

00:03:55.109 --> 00:03:55.735
No.

00:03:58.780 --> 00:03:59.948
This will be the last time.

00:04:01.472 --> 00:04:02.116
For what?

00:04:04.896 --> 00:04:06.663
I won't say it again.

00:04:09.082 --> 00:04:10.124
Say what?

00:04:15.713 --> 00:04:16.839
I like you.

00:04:21.177 --> 00:04:23.596
This is my honest confession.

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:30.270
Do you remember?

00:04:31.187 --> 00:04:32.689
You always talk about cutting ties.

00:04:35.692 --> 00:04:37.735
But I always wanted to play with you.

00:04:40.448 --> 00:04:41.948
But I think

00:04:42.272 --> 00:04:44.492
if we just stay friends,

00:04:45.024 --> 00:04:46.624
I would regret it.

00:04:49.152 --> 00:04:50.999
Maybe from the very beginning,

00:04:50.999 --> 00:04:53.501
my feelings for you
were already decided.

00:05:03.344 --> 00:05:05.054
My feelings

00:05:05.056 --> 00:05:06.681
have never changed.

00:05:08.725 --> 00:05:09.475
It's you.

00:05:10.176 --> 00:05:11.561
Only you.

00:05:13.021 --> 00:05:14.647
And it will always be you.

00:05:27.424 --> 00:05:28.494
I'm leaving now.

00:05:30.592 --> 00:05:31.956
Okay.

00:05:40.214 --> 00:05:41.132
I like you too.

00:06:06.656 --> 00:06:07.742
I'm leaving.

00:06:08.534 --> 00:06:09.452
I love you, honey.

00:06:09.619 --> 00:06:12.163
Be quiet! Just be quiet.

00:06:31.808 --> 00:06:32.558
Why calling?

00:06:33.056 --> 00:06:33.768
I like you.

00:06:34.394 --> 00:06:34.894
Ugh.

00:06:35.353 --> 00:06:36.020
Crazy.

00:06:36.448 --> 00:06:37.248
What are you doing?

00:06:38.147 --> 00:06:39.424
We parted just 5 minutes ago.

00:06:41.567 --> 00:06:43.111
Already 5 minutes?

00:06:43.820 --> 00:06:45.488
It's just too long.

00:06:46.322 --> 00:06:48.866
Washing hands, washing feet,
and missing me.

00:06:50.076 --> 00:06:51.494
My Haneul must be busy, huh?

00:06:51.577 --> 00:06:52.578
Can I get a refund?

00:06:54.122 --> 00:06:55.832
Sorry, no returns, dear customer.

00:06:56.582 --> 00:06:57.834
I'll always be yours.

00:07:05.633 --> 00:07:07.343
I want to see you
early tomorrow morning.

00:07:12.223 --> 00:07:13.266
Nice weather today.

00:07:13.307 --> 00:07:14.392
Ah, I'm so full.

00:07:18.304 --> 00:07:19.680
That place doesn't taste the same.

00:07:20.565 --> 00:07:21.399
Really?

00:07:21.899 --> 00:07:23.067
I feel almost the same.

00:07:24.068 --> 00:07:26.154
Similar and the same, they're different.

00:07:26.654 --> 00:07:28.704
We used to go there often.

00:07:35.204 --> 00:07:36.664
Do people usually hold hands

00:07:37.373 --> 00:07:38.583
on the first date?

00:07:40.418 --> 00:07:42.378
Usually before dating.

00:07:43.421 --> 00:07:43.963
What?

00:07:44.422 --> 00:07:45.006
What's wrong?

00:07:45.465 --> 00:07:47.425
You, old-fashioned guy,
think that's too bold?

00:07:48.384 --> 00:07:49.177
Shut up.

00:08:05.193 --> 00:08:05.776
Cheers.

00:08:05.818 --> 00:08:10.128
(2018, Seven Years Ago, Winter)

00:08:14.577 --> 00:08:15.828
Was filming tiring today?

00:08:16.913 --> 00:08:17.955
You look exhausted.

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:19.582
I shouldn't have asked you out.

00:08:19.957 --> 00:08:20.666
No.

00:08:21.042 --> 00:08:21.834
I'm fine.

00:08:22.251 --> 00:08:24.170
Sounds like a lie.

00:08:26.005 --> 00:08:27.006
By the way,

00:08:27.465 --> 00:08:30.176
I told you last time
that some weird guy registered, right?

00:08:30.635 --> 00:08:32.011
He's over fifty,

00:08:32.428 --> 00:08:34.096
but he asked the girls in our class

00:08:34.222 --> 00:08:35.640
to call him "Oppa".

00:08:36.307 --> 00:08:37.058
Isn't that crazy?

00:08:37.975 --> 00:08:40.811
The girls all came asking for refunds.

00:08:47.026 --> 00:08:48.027
So Jiyoung

00:08:48.486 --> 00:08:50.655
told him she'd refund him
and asked him to leave.

00:08:51.822 --> 00:08:53.324
But he demanded compensation.

00:08:53.491 --> 00:08:54.496
Thirty times the tuition.

00:08:57.036 --> 00:08:58.204
You've worked hard.

00:09:03.167 --> 00:09:07.129
(Such a warm, sunny spring day)

00:09:07.505 --> 00:09:11.300
(makes people want
to stroll hand in hand.)

00:09:11.634 --> 00:09:14.595
(For lovers, it's the perfect date day.)

00:09:16.896 --> 00:09:19.225
(2019, Six Years Ago, Spring)
We can meet another day if you're tired.

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:21.852
Insisted on coming and look exhausted.

00:09:23.271 --> 00:09:24.855
How can I feel good?

00:09:25.064 --> 00:09:26.148
I came because I'm fine.

00:09:26.691 --> 00:09:28.025
Fine?

00:09:29.068 --> 00:09:30.069
Look at your face.

00:09:30.236 --> 00:09:31.404
Why push yourself?

00:09:32.989 --> 00:09:33.906
I didn't.

00:09:34.407 --> 00:09:35.992
I told you I'm fine.

00:09:36.993 --> 00:09:38.077
It's so annoying.

00:09:39.203 --> 00:09:40.246
How can you say that?

00:09:41.455 --> 00:09:43.124
Every time you do this, it annoys me.

00:09:43.624 --> 00:09:44.834
It's not the first time.

00:09:46.210 --> 00:09:47.712
You were hospitalized last time.

00:09:48.640 --> 00:09:50.048
Will we die if we don't meet today?

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:51.340
And break up?

00:09:52.925 --> 00:09:54.135
I came because I missed you.

00:09:54.677 --> 00:09:55.803
Why push me like this?

00:09:57.805 --> 00:09:59.557
Do you remember what I said today?

00:10:00.057 --> 00:10:01.017
Why does that matter?

00:10:01.434 --> 00:10:02.560
Then what matters?

00:10:03.644 --> 00:10:04.812
Why do you want to see me?

00:10:05.563 --> 00:10:06.897
Because I want to be with you.

00:10:08.384 --> 00:10:08.884
Fine.

00:10:12.695 --> 00:10:13.696
We can go home now.

00:10:15.156 --> 00:10:16.198
I'll take the bus.

00:10:17.241 --> 00:10:18.200
Suit yourself.

00:10:22.496 --> 00:10:26.208
(2019, Six Years Ago, Autumn)

00:10:57.536 --> 00:11:01.504
(2020, Five Years Ago, Winter)

00:11:18.344 --> 00:11:23.140
(2021, Four Years Ago, Winter)

00:11:44.578 --> 00:11:47.540
(It's okay to take your time.)

00:11:47.904 --> 00:11:48.833
(I'll wait for you.)

00:12:11.936 --> 00:12:12.898
Gi Haneul.

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:14.176
Let's go together.

00:12:16.193 --> 00:12:16.902
Don't follow me.

00:12:23.424 --> 00:12:25.119
Thanks for walking me home.

00:12:27.663 --> 00:12:28.247
Go on in.

00:12:30.875 --> 00:12:31.542
What?

00:12:31.751 --> 00:12:32.752
I'm sleeping here too.

00:12:33.461 --> 00:12:34.962
Why are you sleeping at my house?

00:12:35.713 --> 00:12:37.631
I haven't had
mother-in-law's cooking for long.

00:12:38.007 --> 00:12:38.632
Perfect.

00:12:39.133 --> 00:12:40.801
Don't call her that.

00:12:41.135 --> 00:12:41.927
What should I?

00:12:42.219 --> 00:12:43.679
She is my mother-in-law.

00:12:44.013 --> 00:12:44.972
Afraid I'd eat you poor?

00:12:48.392 --> 00:12:49.059
Ah!

00:12:49.351 --> 00:12:51.562
I wonder who it is. It's you, Saebyeok.

00:13:00.237 --> 00:13:00.821
Saebyeok.

00:13:01.489 --> 00:13:02.782
Long time no see.

00:13:02.912 --> 00:13:04.200
You came to pick up Haneul?

00:13:04.825 --> 00:13:05.824
Go back to your own home.

00:13:06.619 --> 00:13:08.448
I heard Haneul is staying tonight.

00:13:08.448 --> 00:13:09.952
It's been a while, so I'll stay over.

00:13:09.952 --> 00:13:11.499
Have you had dinner?

00:13:11.916 --> 00:13:13.375
We ate early today.

00:13:13.918 --> 00:13:15.461
It's okay. We already ate.

00:13:16.224 --> 00:13:17.440
What are you filming lately?

00:13:17.888 --> 00:13:19.256
A new drama.

00:13:19.456 --> 00:13:20.704
Really? Who's in it?

00:13:20.704 --> 00:13:21.888
Yonwoo and Sohyun.

00:13:22.718 --> 00:13:23.469
Cha Yonwoo?

00:13:24.470 --> 00:13:26.388
I heard Sohyun is pretty.

00:13:26.931 --> 00:13:27.640
Is that true?

00:13:27.848 --> 00:13:29.058
What "Sohyun"?

00:13:29.350 --> 00:13:30.226
Sounds so tacky.

00:13:30.976 --> 00:13:31.727
What?

00:13:32.061 --> 00:13:33.687
You used to say she was pretty too.

00:13:33.938 --> 00:13:35.136
I don't remember.

00:13:35.904 --> 00:13:36.416
Ah!

00:13:37.440 --> 00:13:38.272
My head hurts!

00:13:38.818 --> 00:13:39.360
Are you okay?

00:13:39.860 --> 00:13:41.237
Didn't you lose a liter of blood?

00:13:42.822 --> 00:13:43.488
You can shut up.

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:45.491
Oh!

00:13:45.950 --> 00:13:47.284
Really a pair of dummies.

00:13:59.104 --> 00:14:00.064
Asleep?

00:14:02.800 --> 00:14:04.093
How could I sleep?

00:14:04.384 --> 00:14:05.302
Why?

00:14:05.970 --> 00:14:06.887
Too excited?

00:14:09.557 --> 00:14:12.810
Since when did you get
such a sharp tongue?

00:14:19.358 --> 00:14:20.526
That's still there.

00:14:22.319 --> 00:14:23.612
You asked not to tear that off.

00:14:24.224 --> 00:14:25.155
Did I?

00:14:26.656 --> 00:14:30.244
You said it was your childhood memory,
even argued with your mom for that.

00:14:31.040 --> 00:14:32.705
In the end, you won.

00:14:34.748 --> 00:14:36.709
Do you remember us putting that up?

00:14:36.896 --> 00:14:37.710
Hmm.

00:14:38.794 --> 00:14:40.838
I asked you to help me.

00:14:40.928 --> 00:14:43.632
You climbed on a chair,

00:14:43.904 --> 00:14:46.594
but I didn't hold it steady. You fell

00:14:46.844 --> 00:14:47.887
and got a fracture.

00:14:49.013 --> 00:14:51.348
Though I was the one hurt,
you were scared of being scolded

00:14:51.348 --> 00:14:52.808
and cried even harder than me.

00:14:53.216 --> 00:14:56.103
Right, I remember.

00:14:57.146 --> 00:14:58.898
Gi Haneul was such a scaredy-cat.

00:15:00.352 --> 00:15:01.650
So cute.

00:15:03.027 --> 00:15:05.988
Stop saying that cheesy word.

00:15:13.996 --> 00:15:15.247
Stop staring at me.

00:15:15.776 --> 00:15:16.874
Just look to the right.

00:15:19.460 --> 00:15:21.712
Everyone should know
you're such a lunatic.

00:15:22.176 --> 00:15:24.632
The true face of a superstar.

00:15:28.093 --> 00:15:30.262
I'm not exactly Mr. Nice Guy now either.

00:15:38.354 --> 00:15:38.896
Yeo Saebyeok.

00:15:39.296 --> 00:15:39.813
Hmm?

00:15:42.107 --> 00:15:43.525
Doesn't it bother you?

00:15:44.416 --> 00:15:45.402
What?

00:15:46.208 --> 00:15:47.905
My amnesia.

00:15:50.366 --> 00:15:53.035
You're carrying all the memories alone.

00:15:54.816 --> 00:15:55.488
I

00:15:56.224 --> 00:15:58.248
can handle anything.

00:16:03.520 --> 00:16:05.839
I might never get my memories back.

00:16:06.656 --> 00:16:08.717
What if I never become

00:16:10.752 --> 00:16:12.054
the old me again?

00:16:13.639 --> 00:16:14.640
It's okay.

00:16:16.892 --> 00:16:18.268
No matter what you become,

00:16:19.395 --> 00:16:21.105
I'll accept.

00:16:29.728 --> 00:16:30.364
I

00:16:31.115 --> 00:16:32.241
won't give up on you.

00:16:47.297 --> 00:16:48.215
Need any help?

00:16:49.088 --> 00:16:51.301
Why are you up so early?

00:16:51.552 --> 00:16:53.345
I have to leave soon.

00:16:54.638 --> 00:16:55.597
Almost there, right?

00:17:07.317 --> 00:17:08.960
Gi Saetbyeol! Gi Haneul!

00:17:08.960 --> 00:17:10.237
Come eat!

00:17:12.489 --> 00:17:13.615
What did you make?

00:17:14.408 --> 00:17:17.036
At your age,
all you think about is eating.

00:17:17.411 --> 00:17:21.540
Well, your son-in-law is here. I wonder
if you made a big feast this early.

00:17:22.656 --> 00:17:23.375
As expected.

00:17:23.744 --> 00:17:25.169
Even royal food can't beat this.

00:17:25.669 --> 00:17:26.712
Saebyeok, I'm eating.

00:17:26.976 --> 00:17:28.608
Mom, thanks for the meal.

00:17:33.984 --> 00:17:35.776
Someone's been calling you all morning.

00:17:35.808 --> 00:17:37.473
From Maumchae, something like that.

00:17:43.770 --> 00:17:45.105
(Jang Jinhui)

00:17:45.105 --> 00:17:48.576
Mr. Jang. We've talked before.

00:17:48.901 --> 00:17:50.400
You still haven't changed your mind?

00:17:51.445 --> 00:17:54.406
Yes. I'll quit the scene
after this project.

00:17:56.617 --> 00:17:57.451
Quit?

00:17:59.036 --> 00:18:00.871
How can you just quit like that?

00:18:01.872 --> 00:18:05.042
I'll finish my current projects and ads.

00:18:07.795 --> 00:18:09.171
Is it because of Hollywood?

00:18:10.047 --> 00:18:12.288
Don't quit. You don't have
to go to Hollywood.

00:18:12.758 --> 00:18:13.984
If I keep doing this job,

00:18:13.984 --> 00:18:16.178
I might not be able to protect Haneul.

00:18:16.576 --> 00:18:18.304
If you quit now,

00:18:18.432 --> 00:18:20.000
do you know how much the loss will be?

00:18:20.849 --> 00:18:22.720
I'll take responsibility

00:18:23.456 --> 00:18:24.895
for anything I need to.

00:18:27.136 --> 00:18:28.857
That's a real pity.

00:18:30.067 --> 00:18:32.694
You just became a top star.

00:18:32.694 --> 00:18:35.531
I became an actor for Haneul anyway.

00:18:35.531 --> 00:18:37.282
If I can't protect him,

00:18:37.282 --> 00:18:39.409
there's no reason to continue.

00:18:41.370 --> 00:18:42.496
You'll regret it.

00:18:43.552 --> 00:18:44.540
I won't.

00:18:45.457 --> 00:18:47.292
The only thing I want is Haneul.

00:19:00.597 --> 00:19:01.723
Did you hear that rumor?

00:19:02.182 --> 00:19:03.058
What rumor?

00:19:03.892 --> 00:19:04.810
I heard Yeo Saebyeok

00:19:05.769 --> 00:19:07.271
is dating Sohyun.

00:19:09.189 --> 00:19:09.898
That's not true.

00:19:11.483 --> 00:19:12.401
Why do you say that?

00:19:13.902 --> 00:19:14.496
He

00:19:14.496 --> 00:19:15.612
isn't that kind of person.

00:19:16.572 --> 00:19:17.614
Who knows?

00:19:18.323 --> 00:19:19.449
You can measure the sea,

00:19:19.658 --> 00:19:21.285
but not a person's heart.

00:19:22.202 --> 00:19:23.078
That man

00:19:23.245 --> 00:19:23.996
is upright

00:19:24.329 --> 00:19:25.205
and sincere.

00:19:26.832 --> 00:19:27.712
You really trust him.

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:29.504
I'm jealous.

00:19:31.003 --> 00:19:32.796
So, it's Sohyun who likes Yeo Saebyeok?

00:19:37.120 --> 00:19:38.135
But

00:19:38.135 --> 00:19:39.636
one-sided love is still love.

00:19:46.496 --> 00:19:47.232
Saebyeok!

00:19:47.232 --> 00:19:48.061
Big trouble.

00:19:48.442 --> 00:19:52.191
(News: Yeo Saebyeok and Sohyun
Are Dating. Agency Remains Silent)

00:19:52.191 --> 00:19:53.504
Ah! Oh, my!

00:19:53.504 --> 00:19:54.985
Who is spreading this nonsense?

00:19:56.111 --> 00:19:56.904
It wasn't you, huh?

00:19:57.792 --> 00:19:59.114
(Incoming call: Reporter Yon)

00:19:59.114 --> 00:20:00.189
Hold on. Let me take this.

00:20:00.782 --> 00:20:01.575
Hello?

00:20:03.834 --> 00:20:05.632
(Haneul)

00:20:27.809 --> 00:20:28.928
Why not answer the phone?

00:20:30.395 --> 00:20:31.021
The phone?

00:20:33.106 --> 00:20:34.066
It's probably in my bag.

00:20:34.358 --> 00:20:35.567
Let's talk.

00:20:37.236 --> 00:20:38.320
I'll take out the trash.

00:20:42.282 --> 00:20:42.908
Just a moment.

00:20:43.936 --> 00:20:44.743
Gi Haneul.

00:20:52.209 --> 00:20:53.056
Wow!

00:20:54.920 --> 00:20:56.338
Stars are really stars.

00:20:57.088 --> 00:20:58.507
The photo looks so great.

00:20:59.466 --> 00:21:02.636
Do actors really fall for each other
while filming?

00:21:03.929 --> 00:21:04.638
Shut up.

00:21:05.055 --> 00:21:05.931
What's wrong?

00:21:06.598 --> 00:21:08.475
Even Haneul said
you two look good together.

00:21:09.309 --> 00:21:09.810
What?

00:21:12.521 --> 00:21:13.855
I showed him the photos.

00:21:14.880 --> 00:21:15.808
Couple of the century.

00:21:16.275 --> 00:21:17.859
Really awesome.

00:21:20.988 --> 00:21:21.780
How does it feel?

00:21:21.780 --> 00:21:22.572
You!

00:21:23.648 --> 00:21:24.950
Yeo Saebyeok.

00:21:25.600 --> 00:21:27.424
Don't lash out at innocent people.
Come here.

00:21:31.415 --> 00:21:32.374
Yeo Saebyeok!

00:21:38.797 --> 00:21:39.381
You...

00:21:40.416 --> 00:21:41.184
Don't come for me.

00:21:41.184 --> 00:21:42.301
Haneul.

00:21:42.301 --> 00:21:43.468
Let me explain.

00:21:43.844 --> 00:21:45.887
No need to explain everything
to me in detail.

00:21:47.889 --> 00:21:49.433
Reporters will follow you.

00:21:50.016 --> 00:21:51.560
Don't drag me into this.

00:21:52.227 --> 00:21:52.894
Go home.

00:21:56.640 --> 00:21:57.824
Handle it all first.

00:21:59.943 --> 00:22:01.069
Call me then.

00:23:02.522 --> 00:23:03.072
Haneul.

00:23:12.800 --> 00:23:13.850
Why hide it from me?

00:23:14.048 --> 00:23:15.328
Let me explain.

00:23:18.980 --> 00:23:19.773
Explain what?

00:23:21.472 --> 00:23:23.652
You've always treated me like an idiot.

00:23:24.444 --> 00:23:25.612
What is there to explain now?

00:23:26.048 --> 00:23:27.322
I did it all for you.

00:23:28.949 --> 00:23:29.658
Liar.

00:23:30.909 --> 00:23:33.328
You're just afraid.

00:23:34.528 --> 00:23:36.623
Afraid of being alone again.

00:23:45.507 --> 00:23:47.384
I never expected that anyway.

00:23:48.468 --> 00:23:50.053
It's all because of you.

00:23:54.141 --> 00:23:55.808
(The unfinished memory from that day...)

00:23:55.808 --> 00:23:56.309
Saebyeok.

00:23:57.216 --> 00:24:00.313
(I kept it as a punishment to myself.)

00:24:02.240 --> 00:24:04.736
Saebyeok,
I really have no confidence left.

00:24:14.048 --> 00:24:15.078
Let's break up.

00:24:15.904 --> 00:24:16.705
Seriously.

00:24:18.976 --> 00:24:19.791
Please.

00:24:23.232 --> 00:24:23.879
Gi Haneul.

00:24:28.425 --> 00:24:29.384
Let's break up.

00:24:43.440 --> 00:24:46.401
(But I never thought
that would hurt you.)

00:24:56.096 --> 00:24:58.288
(Are you still collecting as I said?)

00:24:59.232 --> 00:25:02.167
(This time will be different.)

00:25:11.008 --> 00:25:12.010
Saebyeok.

00:25:13.053 --> 00:25:14.221
You forgot this.

00:25:18.720 --> 00:25:19.456
Kang.

00:25:20.032 --> 00:25:21.728
I'm holding a press conference tomorrow.

00:25:23.063 --> 00:25:23.939
Suddenly?

00:25:27.526 --> 00:25:29.536
Shouldn't you inform the company first?

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:32.544
Kang, do you trust me?

00:25:33.823 --> 00:25:35.075
If you really trust me,

00:25:35.936 --> 00:25:36.992
please help me this once.

00:25:48.088 --> 00:25:51.049
(Reporter Kim)

00:25:55.053 --> 00:25:57.597
Hello? We're at the parking lot now.

00:25:57.973 --> 00:25:58.880
Hello? Director Kang.

00:25:59.140 --> 00:26:02.936
Your company canceled the conference.
All the reporters left.

00:26:03.584 --> 00:26:04.354
What?

00:26:04.354 --> 00:26:05.897
Who contacted them?

00:26:06.112 --> 00:26:08.650
They said Mr. Jang called personally.

00:26:09.152 --> 00:26:10.318
Huh. Anyway...

00:26:10.318 --> 00:26:11.987
There's no one here now.

00:26:11.987 --> 00:26:13.071
I'm hanging up.

00:26:17.568 --> 00:26:18.827
What should we do, Saebyeok?

00:26:19.456 --> 00:26:20.288
Kang.

00:26:20.544 --> 00:26:21.454
Go to the company.

00:26:32.826 --> 00:26:34.336
(CEO's Office)

00:26:34.336 --> 00:26:35.051
Well,

00:26:35.840 --> 00:26:37.512
I'm going to marry Yeo Saebyeok.

00:26:38.432 --> 00:26:39.431
What?

00:26:43.008 --> 00:26:44.480
If you don't want to see the news

00:26:44.480 --> 00:26:47.022
about my marriage
with Yeo Saebyeok at 9 PM tonight,

00:26:48.256 --> 00:26:49.774
stop messing with him.

00:26:50.208 --> 00:26:52.777
Are you threatening me?

00:26:52.896 --> 00:26:55.296
I've seen plenty of people like you.

00:26:55.488 --> 00:26:57.504
Trying to get the benefit from Saebyeok.

00:26:57.504 --> 00:26:59.424
If soft tactics don't work,
you use hard ones,

00:26:59.424 --> 00:27:01.369
even cursing him.

00:27:02.272 --> 00:27:04.748
But they all ignore one thing.

00:27:05.088 --> 00:27:06.333
Do you know what it is?

00:27:07.328 --> 00:27:09.472
Why should I know?

00:27:09.472 --> 00:27:10.837
Yeo Saebyeok

00:27:11.360 --> 00:27:12.839
and I are one.

00:27:13.472 --> 00:27:15.216
If you touch him,

00:27:15.328 --> 00:27:17.218
I won't stand by.

00:27:18.432 --> 00:27:20.221
Even if I've lost my memory,

00:27:20.384 --> 00:27:21.890
that won't change.

00:27:22.336 --> 00:27:23.350
Got it?

00:27:26.688 --> 00:27:27.771
So

00:27:28.320 --> 00:27:29.939
you've been living comfortably

00:27:29.939 --> 00:27:32.400
by his side.

00:27:33.184 --> 00:27:34.861
If you don't want to lose everything,

00:27:34.861 --> 00:27:36.363
please behave.

00:27:36.363 --> 00:27:37.696
Go ahead if you dare.

00:27:37.696 --> 00:27:39.491
You think I'm overestimating myself?

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:41.576
I used to be an athlete.

00:27:41.824 --> 00:27:43.328
I'm very persistent.

00:27:43.328 --> 00:27:44.746
I'm clean.

00:27:44.746 --> 00:27:46.122
You won't find any dirt on me.

00:27:46.122 --> 00:27:48.708
I know the news and the photos
were all fabricated by you.

00:27:49.056 --> 00:27:51.419
If people find out an agency did this,

00:27:51.616 --> 00:27:53.588
do you think other artists will stay?

00:27:54.688 --> 00:27:56.508
Just leave Yeo Saebyeok alone.

00:27:56.928 --> 00:28:00.220
If you push me too far,
I'll expose everything.

00:28:01.920 --> 00:28:03.431
Actually,

00:28:03.776 --> 00:28:05.809
you know nothing
about Yeo Saebyeok at all.

00:28:11.712 --> 00:28:14.025
(CEO's Office)
Let's go. It's all settled.

00:28:29.344 --> 00:28:32.384
(How did you know Mr. Jang planned it?)

00:28:32.384 --> 00:28:34.963
(I did some digging.)

00:28:53.231 --> 00:28:54.899
(To Saebyeok)

00:29:19.040 --> 00:29:23.136
(Long time no see.
I should've finished Gi Haneul sooner)

00:29:36.122 --> 00:29:39.159
♪The more I try to run away♪

00:29:39.457 --> 00:29:41.140
♪The clearer it becomes♪

00:29:42.742 --> 00:29:46.032
♪Even the word "love"♪

00:29:46.328 --> 00:29:47.519
♪Can't convey how I feel♪

00:29:49.588 --> 00:29:52.661
♪Watching your shadow moving forward♪

00:29:52.890 --> 00:29:54.522
♪Sometimes, I resent you♪

00:29:54.522 --> 00:29:56.384
♪But without you,
everything feels strange♪

00:29:56.448 --> 00:30:01.683
♪The pain also makes me grow♪

00:30:03.130 --> 00:30:05.030
♪There is a lot to say♪

00:30:05.030 --> 00:30:06.450
♪Trying to separate us♪

00:30:06.763 --> 00:30:09.608
♪Even if I look like a fool♪

00:30:10.204 --> 00:30:11.724
♪It doesn't matter♪

00:30:11.724 --> 00:30:13.690
♪This is how we are♪

00:30:13.690 --> 00:30:16.605
♪Connected to each other♪

00:30:16.666 --> 00:30:20.185
♪We are truly strange♪

00:30:20.666 --> 00:30:23.717
♪Pushing each other away,
yet embracing again♪

00:30:23.717 --> 00:30:26.010
♪Between love and pain♪

00:30:26.042 --> 00:30:29.053
♪In some corner♪

00:30:29.204 --> 00:30:32.689
♪In the end, we can only be together♪

00:30:39.796 --> 00:30:43.628
♪Because that's us♪

00:30:47.082 --> 00:30:48.442
♪Even if what we said yesterday♪

00:30:48.442 --> 00:30:49.896
♪Remains in the heart♪

00:30:50.074 --> 00:30:51.866
♪As time passes♪

00:30:51.866 --> 00:30:53.082
♪Maybe I'll laugh about it♪

00:30:53.082 --> 00:30:55.162
♪Even those painful memories♪

00:30:55.162 --> 00:30:56.282
♪Are also ours♪

00:30:56.436 --> 00:30:59.016
♪Seems we can♪

00:30:59.016 --> 00:31:00.953
♪Be more understanding♪

00:31:01.428 --> 00:31:03.612
♪I clearly told myself♪

00:31:04.634 --> 00:31:06.892
♪Never to see you again♪

00:31:07.130 --> 00:31:09.839
♪But hearing your voice♪

00:31:10.196 --> 00:31:11.226
♪I completely break down♪